<p>On March 31, Senator Booker <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cory_Booker%27s_marathon_speech">set the record</a> for the longest-ever Senate speech, at 25 hours and 5 minutes, and rallied the nation against Trump’s violation of our democracy.
He received <a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress/cory-booker-speech-ignites-democrats-desperate-fighter-rcna199204">350 million likes on TikTok</a>, 28,000 thankful phone calls, and his words are still heard today: “it’s not about left versus right, it’s about right versus wrong!”</p>